OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy and wet with some rain
OL,7,Fand fog patches affecting the region.
OL,8,FThe rain can be heavy for a time
OL,9,Faround midnight, but will slowly peter
OL,10,Fout by dawn, though staying rather
OL,11,Fcloudy. Mild, though breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FTuesday morning looks cloudy
OL,14,Fand breezy with patchy light rain,
OL,15,Fmostly in the west. Some brighter
OL,16,Fspells are possible later, especially
OL,17,Fin the east where it will become very
OL,18,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
