OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FAnother very mild, though fairly
OL,7,Fcloudy day on Wednesday with some rain
OL,8,Fin the west. Cooling down thereafter
OL,9,Fand turning more unsettled with rain
OL,10,Fand strong winds possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
